      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>530 - Additional Physical Form Available Note (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2001</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Undefined</em><br># - Undefined <br><br></td>
