      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> - Field 530 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present.
      </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="font_small"><em>$u - Uniform Resource Identifier [NEW, 2000]</em><br><em>$z - Source of note information (AM, CF, VM, SE) [OBSOLETE, 1990]</em><br>Source information is included as part of the related availability or order number
                        information in subfields $a-$d.
      </div>
